{"tid":855803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遭堆高機砸爆頭慘死. 今次圖＋片","createTime":"2018-10-10T09:11:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T11:38:33.000Z","uid":72009,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ee332b9eb4ce30e139292926286bb96a69f7d136","tid":855803,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T09:11:58.000Z","msg":"中國一名工人10月8日在用堆高機將貨物裝上貨車時，只是因為卸貨後沒有將堆高機貨叉移回下方，結果拉著堆高機進工廠時堆高機翻覆，工人回身想用雙臂阻擋，但根本無法對抗堆高機的重量，結果被砸爆頭慘死。<br />\n<br />\n這起工安意外的監視器影片在微博瘋傳，當時工人用堆高機將貨物放入貨車後，順手便直接將堆高機往工廠裡拖，但經過內外交界處地面有一點不平整，而堆高機此時重心又在偏上方，小小的震動就讓堆高機翻覆，工人轉身伸手阻擋但仍慘遭砸死。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20181010/1445238\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20181010%2F1445238&d=d%2F%2Bhen19C%2BT4pq%2BgCYCsjDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=88bade11\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20181010%2F1445238&h=0e9df6a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20181010/1445238</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181010/640_9770ad24fb91e5b432f8aa39cba7d535.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181010%2F640_9770ad24fb91e5b432f8aa39cba7d535.jpg&h=46eb40ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181010/640_8cb1cc153a25d224be406cbe37991522.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181010%2F640_8cb1cc153a25d224be406cbe37991522.jpg&h=a194e35e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95630454713b8f31ac1ea339758a8a0bd4c6a527","tid":855803,"uid":19126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T09:15:18.000Z","msg":"白痴仔用手擋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當年懶型拉住架唧車落條小斜覺得唔對路都即刻走開，做過下運輸，完全知道唔可以同啲貨、唧車鏟車鬥力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5403850dc67f599d000a4a44c7d2fead283895f","tid":855803,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T09:17:41.000Z","msg":"咁叫爆頭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"138a66aaa43ce833bba29cad18f5a122ce3b1160","tid":855803,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T09:17:57.000Z","msg":"扮美國隊長？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f896fb7db0bbb441c896a9fe7683846b8580d4ce","tid":855803,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T11:38:33.000Z","msg":"睇落好輕喎"}]}